a little advice.

380
00:13:46,553 --> 00:13:48,420
Well, listen here,
sweet face.

381
00:13:48,422 --> 00:13:50,055
I get it.

382
00:13:50,057 --> 00:13:51,156
You're the it girl.

383
00:13:51,158 --> 00:13:53,291
Well, you know who I am?

384
00:13:53,293 --> 00:13:54,659
I'm Litt man.

385
00:13:54,661 --> 00:13:57,462
