411
00:15:07,553 --> 00:15:09,753
Katrina's never missed
a meeting in her life.

412
00:15:09,755 --> 00:15:10,954
If she's not there,
she will be.

413
00:15:10,956 --> 00:15:11,755
Just go ahead and start.
